doc.title: Link Open With ka ɲɛfɔli kunbaba
doc.description:
Nin ​​farankan in b’a to i bɛ se ka hyperlinkw dabɔcogo kɔlɔsi nɔgɔya la .

Fɛntɛri : navigatɔrɔ wɛrɛw, pop-up windows, windows kura, incognito windows kura, finɛtiri sisan (default)

Tabw : sisan tab kinin fɛ, sisan tab kinin fɛ, sisan tab kinin fɛ (dafalen)

Waleya cogoya : baarakɛbali, baara kɛ joona (dafalen)
